name: CHARITY //elephant poster
description:
this poster comes out of one of my illustration works made at the beginning of 2013-
please click to zoom the details.

52cm x 80cm
20.47" x 31.5"

THE ENTIRE AMOUNT OUT OF THE PURCHASE OF THIS PRINT GOES TO ORGANISATIONS WHO TAKE CARE OF STRAY DOGS IN SERBIA.THE SITUATION IS MUCH TRAGIC AS IN MANY BALCAN COUNTRIES.

I HAVE LOWERED SIGNIFICANTLY THE PRICE OF THESE PRINTS(PREVIOUSLY 65 USD) AND ALL THE ECONOMIC EFFORT OF MAKING THEM I HAVE TAKEN ON MY OWN AS IN THIS WAY I'M HOPING TO SELL MORE OF THESE PRINTS AND HELP MORE OF THE ORGANISATIONS AND PEOPLE WHO FIGHT THE ENORMOUS INDIFFERENCE THAT COMES FROM LOCAL LAW.

AS IN EVERY DIFFICULT SITUATION THERE ARE PEOPLE WHO FIGHT FOR GOOD.PLEASE KEEP IN MIND THAT THE AVERGE MONTH PAY OF A SERBIAN CITIZEN RANGES FROM 200 TO 400 EUROS.SPAYING THE DOG COSTS 60-80€.

THIS IS A BEAUTIFUL PRINT AND WHEN YOU BUY IT, YOU DO GOOD TO YOURSELF, TO A DOG THAT'S ABANDONED AND HUNGRY AND TO A PERSON WHO TAKES CARE OF A DOG.AND AT THE END TO ME.THANK YOU.

MORE ON MY BLOG ABOUT THIS AND THE ORGANISATIONS.

http://thegoodmachinery.bigcartel.com/blog

ONE OF ARTICLES FROM OIPA/INTERNATIONAL ORGANISATION FOR ANIMAL PROTECTION. 

http://www.oipa.org/international/abandonment/campaign/serbia/introduction.htm

it's actually a print made with archival high quality pigments.
the particularity of this type of printing on large scale is that the dispersion of ink depends on humidity in the air & warmth, which makes that each print has it's own shade of cyan slightly different.
this makes each print unique and i think it is perfect.
each scratch, shadow, finger print of charcoal in original drawing, featured on print is intentional and not print mislead.

ships rolled in a sturdy craft tube.
